  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">If <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"the fraction with numerator the square root of x to the fifth power, end root, and denominator the cube root of x to the fourth power, end root, end fraction, equals x raised to the fraction a over b power \"></span></span> for all positive values of <span class=\"italic\">x</span>, what is the value of <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"the fraction a over b\"></span></span>?</p>\n",
  "answerOptions": [],
  "keys": [],
  "rationale": "<p>The correct answer is <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"7 over 6\"></span>. The value of <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"a, over b \"></span> can be found by first rewriting the left-hand side of the given equation as <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"the fraction with numerator x raised to the five halves power, and denominator x raised to the four thirds power, end fraction \"></span>. Using the properties of exponents, this expression can be rewritten as <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x raised to the open parenthesis, five halves, minus four thirds, close parenthesis, power\"></span>. This expression can be rewritten by subtracting the fractions in the exponent, which yields <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x raised to the fraction 7 over 6, power\"></span>. Thus, <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"a, over b \"></span> is <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"7 over 6\"></span>. Note that 7/6, 1.166, and 1.167 are examples of ways to enter a correct answer.</p>\n",
